711520f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Avenue - 19th Street (East)
711520f-a.text:
241-243 East 19th Street, adjoining the N.W. corner of Second
Avenue, showing also the doorway of No. 245, which is the side entrance
to 329 Second Avenue. These buildings will still stand in 1935.
About 1915.
James Suydam.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

707795f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Ave. - 19th St. E.
707795f-a.text:
Second Avenue, west side, from East 19th to 20th St's.,
showing the Florida Apartments occupying this frontage.
April 26, 1940
Ceorge D. Chinn
NO REPRODUCTIONS
